snippet.title: Gachaminer.io - Crypto Mining Simulator | Beta 1.0.0 Gameplay and A Brief Tutorial Part (1)
snippet.description:
Sign Up for your first miner and experience the world of cryptomining.
https://gachaminer.io/ref/306

GachaMiner is an online crypto mining simulator where you can play with other players to mine crypto. Besides, you can fly to other countries and travel to other cities to see other players around the world. This is Beta 1.0.0 gameplay. At the beginning of the game, each player will have to select a mining location and after that will have a miner for free. 

You may take a look if you missed the Alpha Version 🎃
https://youtu.be/rTImCSGeHM8
